        "name": "Entreat Spirit",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You invite a spirit you\u2019ve bonded with to bolster your mind. You gain a +1 status bonus to an Intelligence-, Wisdom-, or Charisma-based skill of your choice. Additionally, you gain a +1 status bonus to saving throws against curse, death, emotion, and fear effects.",
